com.udeyrishi.androidelasticsearchdatamanager.queries

Class CachedQueryExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.udeyrishi.androidelasticsearchdatamanager.queries.CachedQueryExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryExecutor

    public class CachedQueryExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryExecutor
    A QueryExecutor that uses an inner QueryExecutor to obtain results, and caches the results. For subsequent requests, if an IOException is thrown, the cache is used to obtain the results. Created by rishi on 15-11-28.
